sentences: In the 1920s he played in the Ten Foot Band in Chicago.
He played in The Wolverines in 1924 alongside Bix Beiderbecke, where he made his first recordings, and later joined the band of Arnold Johnson.
In 1927 he moved to New York City, where he played in the Paul Whiteman Orchestra until 1931.
